WEBVTT

00:02.068 --> 00:04.954
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:04.954 --> 00:06.456
Yeah, it says here

00:06.456 --> 00:08.458
there's another sighting
of the Loch Ness monster.

00:08.458 --> 00:09.959
Yeah? Do you believe that?

00:09.959 --> 00:11.461
There's even a picture of him.

00:11.461 --> 00:13.463
Whoa! Looks kind of
like President Reagan.

00:13.463 --> 00:14.414
That is Reagan.

00:14.414 --> 00:16.416
The other picture's the monster.

00:16.416 --> 00:17.417
Oh, I see.

00:19.919 --> 00:21.921
Wonder if they'll ever
catch that thing, huh?

00:21.921 --> 00:23.923
Well, I, for one, hope they never do.

00:23.923 --> 00:25.925
I mean, none of us really want to see

00:25.925 --> 00:28.428
that poor beast hauled out of the water

00:28.428 --> 00:30.430
and put on display in some sideshow.

00:30.430 --> 00:31.431
Well, I sure would.

00:31.431 --> 00:33.433
You know, we could all go together.

00:33.433 --> 00:34.434
I don't mind driving.

00:34.434 --> 00:36.436
Yeah, but, uh, you see, Woody, they...

00:36.436 --> 00:37.437
You know, it'd be kind of fun.

00:37.437 --> 00:38.438
We could pack a lunch.

00:38.438 --> 00:39.906
No, Woody, they...

00:39.906 --> 00:40.907
All right, who wants
peanut butter and jelly

00:40.907 --> 00:42.158
and who wants bologna?

00:42.158 --> 00:43.493
Woody, they...

00:43.493 --> 00:45.495
I'll have one of each, all right?

00:46.863 --> 00:51.284
(piano plays)

00:51.284 --> 00:53.703
? Making your way in the world today ?

00:53.703 --> 00:56.706
? Takes everything you've got ?

00:56.706 --> 00:59.209
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

00:59.209 --> 01:02.712
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:02.712 --> 01:08.885
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:08.885 --> 01:10.386
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:10.386 --> 01:15.892
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:16.392 --> 01:20.897
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:20.897 --> 01:23.399
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:23.399 --> 01:25.902
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:25.902 --> 01:30.907
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:31.407 --> 01:33.409
? You want to go where people know ?

01:33.910 --> 01:36.412
? People are all the same ?

01:36.412 --> 01:40.416
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

